<title>JAPAN: Hamamatsu Photonics to issue 10 bln yen CB.</title>
<headline>Hamamatsu Photonics to issue 10 bln yen CB.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>BORROWER - Hamamatsu Photonics Co Ltd</p>
<p>LEAD MGR - Nikko Securities Co Ltd</p>
<p>TRUSTEE - Asahi Bank Ltd</p>
<p> TYPE convertible     ISSUE NO   2	  AMT   10 bln yen</p>
<p> COUPON		   ISS PRICE	     MATURITY 30.Sep.04</p>
